data.description: *** ASSUMABLE  VA LOAN AT 3% RATE TO ELIGIBLE VETERAN OR ACTIVE DUTY BUYERS  *** Experience the pinnacle of sophisticated urban living in the heart of Park View, DC, with this exceptional Penthouse condo. This luxurious residence encompasses two levels of contemporary design, offering 2 bedrooms, 2.5 baths and an array of modern amenities that redefine comfort and convenience. Step inside and be embraced by the warm elegance of hardwood floors that grace both levels. The open-concept living space boasts high ceilings that create an inviting and airy atmosphere, complemented by an abundance of natural light streaming in through expansive windows. To enhance your lifestyle, the condo is equipped with Bluetooth-ready home speakers, allowing you to effortlessly set the mood with your favorite tunes and enjoy an immersive audio experience throughout the space.  On the main floor, you'll discover two generously proportioned bedrooms, each accompanied by its own en-suite bathroom. These private retreats offer a sanctuary of relaxation and luxury, featuring contemporary fixtures and finishes that epitomize modern design sensibilities.  Enjoy the convenience with automated remote control shades that effortlessly adjust to your desired level of privacy and lighting. With a touch of a button, you can transform the ambiance of any room according to your mood or time of day. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's dream, showcasing top-of-the-line appliances, sleek cabinetry, and pristine quartz countertops. Engage in culinary creativity while guests gather around the stylish breakfast bar, fostering an inviting and interactive atmosphere.  Venture to the upper level and discover an additional den or office space, providing the perfect environment for productivity or leisure. This versatile area can be tailored to your needs, whether you require a quiet workspace or a cozy reading nook. The spacious living room on this level is an entertainment haven, ready to accommodate gatherings and create lasting memories. Unwind and revel on your private rooftop terrace, a haven of tranquility above the bustling cityscape. This exclusive outdoor oasis invites you to savor sunsets, host soirées, or simply bask in the serenity of your surroundings. Parking is a breeze with your assigned parking space, ensuring both convenience and security for your vehicles. Located in the heart of Park View, you're surrounded by a vibrant community brimming with diverse dining options, entertainment venues, and cultural experiences. Embrace the local parks, coffee shops, and seamless access to transportation, all contributing to a dynamic urban lifestyle. This Penthouse  represents the epitome of luxurious living, where modern amenities harmonize with an exceptional location.  Elevate your lifestyle and immerse yourself in the sophistication of this Park View, DC masterpiece. Welcome Home!
